window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Book four in the Gaunt's Ghosts series.</b></p> <p>Sent to retrieve holy artefacts from a world lost to Chaos, Gauntâ€™s Ghosts find themselves beset by the enemy...but is Saint Sabbat herself helping them from beyond the grave?</p> <p><b>Listen to it because: </b>it's a new start for Gaunt's Ghosts. With a whole load of new troopers in the regiment and a dangerous mission - a race against time to retrieve holy relics from a dying world - Gaunt and his men (and women now!) have their work cut out for them.</p> <p><b>The story: i</b>n disgrace after a catastrophic war, Colonel-Commissar Ibram Gaunt and the Tanith First are sent to retrieve precious artefacts from a world lost to Chaos. With enemy all around them and time against them, Gaunt's Ghosts and their allies must prevent the holy relics of Saint Sabbat from falling into their foes' hands, and as mysterious events begin to occur, Gaunt begins to suspect that the Saint herself might be aiding them from beyond the grave.</p> <p>Running time 10 hours 13 minutes.</p>"; 
